<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.1">
<l>muṟṟa mūttuk kōṟṟu ṇaiyā muṉṉaṭi nōkkivaḷain</l>
<l>tiṟṟa kāṟpōl taḷḷi meḷḷa viruntaṅ kiḷaiyāmuṉ</l>
<l>peṟṟa tāypōl vanta pēycci perumu laiyūṭuyirai</l>
<l>vaṟṟa vāṅki yuṇṭa vāyāṉ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before [I] can waste away, [just] sitting there quietly,</l>
<l rend="indent">[or] shuffling like [my] legs are frail, bending [over],</l>
<l>Watching [each] step ahead with a cane as an aid, being utterly aged,</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī the one whose mouth sucked</l>
<l rend="indent">and sapped out the life</l>
<l>Within the huge breasts of the demoness who came like a birth mother.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
